<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Contact & Support - Terp Notes</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <header class="topbar">
        <h2>Terp Notes</h2>
        <div class="user-info">
            <% if (user) { %>
                Welcome, <strong>
                    <%= user.firstname %>
                </strong> |
                <a href="/dashboard" class="logout-btn">Dashboard</a> |
                <a href="/logout" class="logout-btn">Logout</a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/" class="logout-btn">Home</a> |
                    <a href="/login" class="logout-btn">Login</a>
                    <% } %>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container" style="max-width: 800px; padding: 3rem 2rem;">
        <h1>Contact & Support</h1>
        <p style="color: #6B7280; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            Need help? Have questions? We're here to assist!
        </p>

        <div class="legal-content">
            <!-- FAQ Section -->
            <section style="background: #F3F4F6; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                <h2>üìö Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

                <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                    <h3>How do I verify my email?</h3>
                    <p>After registration, check your inbox (and spam folder) for a verification email. Click the link
                        to activate your account. If you didn't receive it, click "Resend Verification" on the
                        unverified page.</p>
                </div>

                <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                    <h3>I forgot my password. What do I do?</h3>
                    <p>Click "Forgot Password?" on the login page, enter your email, and we'll send you a password reset
                        link.</p>
                </div>

                <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                    <h3>Can I change my username?</h3>
                    <p>No, usernames are permanent once created. This is to maintain accountability for uploaded
                        content.</p>
                </div>

                <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                    <h3>What file types can I upload?</h3>
                    <p>We support: PDFs, Office documents (.docx, .pptx, .xlsx), images (.jpg, .png, .gif, .svg), text
                        files (.txt, .md), code files (.py, .java, .c, .cpp, .js, .html, .css), and .zip archives.</p>
                </div>

                <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                    <h3>How do I report inappropriate content?</h3>
                    <p>Click the "üö© Report" button on any file card and select a reason. Admins will review and take
                        action.</p>
                </div>

                <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                    <h3>My account is in "view-only" mode. Why?</h3>
                    <p>Your upload privileges have been restricted by an admin, typically due to policy violations.
                        Contact support to request a review.</p>
                </div>

                <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                    <h3>Is this platform affiliated with UMD?</h3>
                    <p><strong>No.</strong> Terp Notes is an independent, student-run platform. We are not affiliated
                        with, endorsed by, or officially connected to the University of Maryland or any educational
                        institution.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Contact Form -->
            <section>
                <h2>‚úâÔ∏è Send Us a Message</h2>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    For issues not covered in the FAQ, fill out the form below and we'll get back to you within 24-48
                    hours.
                </p>

                <form action="/contact/submit" method="POST" class="contact-form"
                    style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="name">Your Name <span style="color: var(--umd-red);">*</span></label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="Enter your name"
                            style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #D1D5DB; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem;">
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                        <label for="email">Your Email <span style="color: var(--umd-red);">*</span></label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="your.email@umd.edu"
                            style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #D1D5DB; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem;">
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                        <label for="subject">Subject <span style="color: var(--umd-red);">*</span></label>
                        <select id="subject" name="subject" required
                            style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #D1D5DB; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem;">
                            <option value="">Select a topic...</option>
                            <option value="account">Account Issues</option>
                            <option value="upload">Upload Problems</option>
                            <option value="bug">Bug Report</option>
                            <option value="content">Content Violation</option>
                            <option value="feature">Feature Request</option>
                            <option value="other">Other</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                        <label for="message">Message <span style="color: var(--umd-red);">*</span></label>
                        <textarea id="message" name="message" required rows="6"
                            placeholder="Describe your issue or question in detail..."
                            style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #D1D5DB; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; resize: vertical;"></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit" class="button primary" style="margin-top: 1.5rem; width: 100%;">
                        Send Message
                    </button>
                </form>
            </section>

            <!-- Direct Contact Info -->
            <section style="margin-top: 3rem; background: #EFF6FF; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px;">
                <h2>üìß Direct Contact</h2>
                <p>
                    For urgent security issues or abuse reports, you can also email us directly at:
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--umd-red); margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <a href="mailto:<%= process.env.EMAIL_USER || 'pmachre@terpmail.umd.edu' %>"
                        style="color: var(--umd-red);">
                        <%= process.env.EMAIL_USER || 'pmachre@terpmail.umd.edu' %>
                    </a>
                </p>
                <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6B7280;">
                    <strong>Note:</strong> Please include your username and a detailed description of the issue.
                </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Platform Status -->
            <section
                style="margin-top: 2rem; text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem; background: #D1FAE5; border-radius: 12px;">
                <h3>Platform Status</h3>
                <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                    <span
                        style="display: inline-block; width: 12px; height: 12px; background: #10B981; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 8px;"></span>
                    All Systems Operational
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6B7280; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                    Check back here for maintenance updates and known issues.
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Terp Notes |
                <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> |
                <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a> |
                <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        </p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>
